structure.unit: STATE LIBRARIES -- LIBRARIANS -- STATE ARCHIVES AND RECORDS

law.history: Repealed 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 61, sec. 12. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 31. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 156. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2450-1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: College libraries, librarian to furnish certain books.
